IC:
:: Rodimus Prime ::

Rodimus was tired after the battle and overseeing the repair. Ultra 
Magnus hadn't answered him so he decided to go rest a bit. On his way 
into the base he runs into Nightlight.

Rodimus Prime: Hey honey. I'm going to get some shut eye.

He pulled her to him, and put his around her.

Rodimus Prime: How about you come with me?

Rodimus kisses her.

:: Kup ::

Kup arrives at Razael's quarters, and knocks.

Kup: Razael? It's Kup, love.

:: Wolfenstein ::

Wolf starts to head out of the Predacon base.

Wolfenstein: Let's go check out those black and white guys. C'mon! 
Beast mode!

Wolf transformes and heads out towards the nWo base.

:: Darkangel ::

Darkangel looks out of the Tripredacus ship, at Earth. Soon it would 
all belong to them, as Cybertron fell.

:: Razor ::

Razor looks over the newcomer to the nWo.

Razor: Well, Heartbreak, welcome to the New World Order. This here is 
your new family. Whern you are in the nWo these bots are your 
brothers, understand?

:: Heartbreak ::

Heartbreak: I do. Thanks for allowing me into this group.

Heartbreak sits down and has some energin with the others.

:: Diesel ::

Diesel chuckled. The nWo just kept getting larger and more powerfull. 
They were truely a force to be reckoned with.
